config PACKAGE_LIBS_LIBANTLR3C
	bool "libantlr3, C runtime"
	select PACKAGE_BUILD_TOOLS_AUTOCONF
	select PACKAGE_BUILD_TOOLS_AUTOMAKE
	help
	  ANTLR, ANother Tool for Language Recognition, is a language tool that
	  provides a framework for constructing recognizers, compilers, and
	  translators from grammatical descriptions. This package contains the
	  development files needed to build the applications using parsers
	  generated by ANTLR in the C language.
